你小學未畢業唔知失踨同失聯有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n失去蹤影 啫你搵佢唔到<br />\n失去聯絡 你都係搵佢唔到<br />\n難道佢失蹤你又聯絡到佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你都聯絡到佢 佢又點失蹤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495021445eb623f52e5d444dad3ecd4ab7965a33","tid":482532,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔用失聯應該用咩？ 失去聯絡？</blockquote><br />\n無失聯之前用咩字咪用番<br />\n小學未畢業？<br />\n定啱啱落嚟香港唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面話用失踨 但失踨同失聯意思唔同架喎 冇失聯之前咪用失去聯絡囉 到底有乜問題 定你小學未畢業唔知失踨同失聯有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n失去蹤影 啫你搵佢唔到<br />\n失去聯絡 你都係搵佢唔到<br />\n難道佢失蹤你又聯絡到佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你都聯絡到佢 佢又點失蹤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://jonathanovsky.wordpress.com/2015/01/01/%E5%A4%B1%E8%81%AF%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E5%8C%AA%E8%AA%9E%E3%80%8D%E5%98%9B%EF%BC%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjonathanovsky.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F01%2F01%2F%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%258C%25AA%25E8%25AA%259E%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2598%259B%25EF%25BC%259F%2F&d=y%2BZDlISUvbTxSxmXlt41VTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=bb7cc8b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jonathanovsky.wordpress.com/2015/01/01/%E5%A4%B1%E8%81%AF%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E5%8C%AA%E8%AA%9E%E3%80%8D%E5%98%9B%EF%BC%9F/</a>"},{"pid":"f7b068e686e27a4e1873dcb9c5c890526febafac","tid":482532,"uid":160010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔用失聯應該用咩？ 失去聯絡？</blockquote><br />\n無失聯之前用咩字咪用番<br />\n小學未畢業？<br />\n定啱啱落嚟香港唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面話用失踨 但失踨同失聯意思唔同架喎 冇失聯之前咪用失去聯絡囉 到底有乜問題 定你小學未畢業唔知失踨同失聯有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n失去蹤影 啫你搵佢唔到<br />\n失去聯絡 你都係搵佢唔到<br />\n難道佢失蹤你又聯絡到佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你都聯絡到佢 佢又點失蹤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲人屌馬航單野應該用失蹤我都明 因為真係完全消失 但呢單野淨係教育局搵唔到人 係佢地老豆老母唔想理教育局姐 班𡃁仔冇失蹤冇消失喎 suppose佢屋企人係見到佢嘛 <br />\n當你有frd有心避你搞到你搵唔到佢 你唔通同人講佢失蹤咩 最多話聯絡唔到佢啫 <br />\n所以而家話佢地同教育局失去聯絡其實係準確過話佢地失蹤架喎"},{"pid":"9a896161daac6b29a16aeb7620ba2c85e9fa4e91","tid":482532,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:48:57.000Z","msg":"失戀💔關人撚事咩"},{"pid":"41624983a1b549126f010a866af2630100b6ef2f","tid":482532,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"失咩聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1768e7664494109fc7cc69cdc944bd11ee77d36f","tid":482532,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢度班on9連咩用詞都要管</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你隻鍵盤捐血五毛蠢撚過閪咁嘅柒樣 縮返入你老母個狗閪入面啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦你"},{"pid":"933b49d2f1499d3f2b44782fa9c3c92596e5d3da","tid":482532,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:38:22.000Z","msg":"用咩字都唔得<br />\n文字獄呀而家"},{"pid":"e99a33ff07e4f72e59a2ab16720c02929d168fbe","tid":482532,"uid":57023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:55:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失咩聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實失蹤已包含失聯的意思，但失聯唔表示失蹤，唔明依加媒體會用失聯呢個詞，唔係好表達失蹤的意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b721cddab24b0d6e2b4b3c3030e889e87c7358d1","tid":482532,"uid":35696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔用失聯應該用咩？ 失去聯絡？</blockquote><br />\n無失聯之前用咩字咪用番<br />\n小學未畢業？<br />\n定啱啱落嚟香港唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面話用失踨 但失踨同失聯意思唔同架喎 冇失聯之前咪用失去聯絡囉 到底有乜問題 定你小學未畢業唔知失踨同失聯有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n失去蹤影 啫你搵佢唔到<br />\n失去聯絡 你都係搵佢唔到<br />\n難道佢失蹤你又聯絡到佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你都聯絡到佢 佢又點失蹤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲人屌馬航單野應該用失蹤我都明 因為真係完全消失 但呢單野淨係教育局搵唔到人 係佢地老豆老母唔想理教育局姐 班𡃁仔冇失蹤冇消失喎 suppose佢屋企人係見到佢嘛 <br />\n當你有frd有心避你搞到你搵唔到佢 你唔通同人講佢失蹤咩 最多話聯絡唔到佢啫 <br />\n所以而家話佢地同教育局失去聯絡其實係準確過話佢地失蹤架喎</blockquote><br />\n應該係無法聯絡<br />\n失去聯絡&lt;意味住本身係有保持聯絡<br />\n咁係呢件事上，教育局係發現學生冇返學，先至嘗試第一次聯絡，所以我認為失去聯絡係用得唔啱"},{"pid":"a56de3dfef3d825fc880fa8878305d34a1bfde2f","tid":482532,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:39:42.000Z","msg":"失去聯絡<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打多兩隻字唔係好難咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1242ec36dc62e734ec1bcc040f9bb84a0b61eee","tid":482532,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係乜鬼狗屎垃圾都做到記者"}]}